name: Impact (itch) (5hadowduck)
description:
Drive through these wild streets! Smash the trashcans and collect the coins! But avoid the other cars or else it's Game Over.

Use A & D, or the Arrow Keys to move your car from side to side in order to avoid obstacles. 

Download the desktop version for higher res gameplay.
